com.unboundid.asn1

Class ASN1UTF8String

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unboundid.asn1.ASN1Element
      • com.unboundid.asn1.ASN1UTF8String
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @NotMutable
 @ThreadSafety(level=COMPLETELY_THREADSAFE)
public final class ASN1UTF8String
extends ASN1Element
    This class provides an ASN.1 UTF-8 string element that can hold any string value that can be represented in the UTF-8 encoding.
    See Also:
